# Display Targets

When the user refers to computer-specific layout or viewport changes in this project, use these saved targets:

- "המחשב שלי" / my computer: viewport `1512x949`, `devicePixelRatio` 2, screen `1512x982`.
- "מחשב ההגשה" / submission computer: viewport `2048x1152`, `devicePixelRatio` 2, screen `2048x1152`.

The submission computer is the most important target. Prioritize it when there is a responsive layout tradeoff.
